fields.Sentence:
Goal is to make money via investing and trading being in line with ESG. The tools that would bring where we want to be:
(i) Continuous learning via Learning Center. 
(ii) Deep Dive into companies via Equity Research. 
(iii) Get a sense around where Markets & Economy going via Market Outlook.
And bringing all together to come up with right ideas and strategies to eventually make money

Bdy2101.com does not provide investment advice. Information is for education purposes.

El objetivo es ganar dinero invirtiendo y negociando en lonea con ESG. Las herramientas que nos llevaroan a donde queremos estar 
(i) Aprendizaje continuo a travos del Centro de aprendizaje 
(ii) Profundizacion en las empresas a travos de Equity Research  
(iii) Tener una idea de hacia donde se dirigen los mercados y la economia a travos de Market Outlook."

Amac  ESG ile uyumlu olarak yatirim ve ticaret yoluyla para kazanmaktir. 
(i) Ogrenim Merkezi aracciligi ile  surekli ogrenme 
(ii) Sermaye Arastirmasi yoluyla sirketlere derinlemesine dalis  
(iii) Piyasa Ongorusu ile Piyasalar ve Ekonominin nereye gittigi hakkinda bir fikir edinin."
